    title: "Google’s TV Streamer 4K is $25 off, its best price ever",
    summary: "The Google TV Streamer 4K is more than just a terrific streaming device. It can also act as a smart home hub, letting you control all major smart home devices directly from your TV. Thanks to Prime Day, it&#8217;s now on sale for $74.99 at Amazon for Prime members, matching its best price to date. [&#8230;]",
    body: "The Google TV Streamer 4K is more than just a terrific streaming device. It can also act as a smart home hub, letting you control all major smart home devices directly from your TV. Thanks to Prime Day, it&#8217;s now on sale for $74.99 at Amazon for Prime members, matching its best price to date. The streamer usually retails for $99.99, making this a $25 discount. If you don’t subscribe to Prime, it’s just $5 more at Best Buy and direct from Google .\n\nGoogle TV Streamer (4K) Where to Buy: $99.99 $74.99 at Amazon (with Prime) $99.99 $79.99 at Google $99.99 $79.99 at Best Buy The Google TV Streamer 4K is a great fit for people already invested in Google&#8217;s ecosystem. The device lets you control your TV with your voice via Gemini, while the Google TV interface pulls recommendations from across your streaming services and even displays Rotten Tomatoes scores.\n\nSetup is also quick and straightforward, taking only about 10 minutes in our testing. One particularly nice touch is that Google asks which streaming services you subscribe to during setup and then downloads the relevant apps for you, so you don&#8217;t have to install them one by one. Beyond streaming, the device doubles as a Matter-compatible smart home hub, making it easy to check your front door camera when the doorbell rings, turn off the lights, or adjust compatible thermostats and other smart devices without getting up.\n\nGoogle has also added a few extra conveniences, including a remote-finder function and an ethernet port for a more reliable connection. Read our Google TV Streamer 4K review . window.HYPE_DESK_CONFIG = { productImageUrl: \"https://platform.theverge.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2026/06/-Human-Pet-Interaction.jpg\", productImageAlt: \"Dreame D30 Ultra CE Robot Vacuum and Mop\", productTitle: \"Dreame D30 Ultra CE Robot Vacuum and Mop\", shortDescription: \"A robot vacuum built for pet owners who are tired of doing it themselves.\", longDescription: \"Built specifically for homes with pets, the D30 Ultra CE brings strong suction to carpet cleaning and handles pet hair without the constant manual intervention most robot vacuums require.\n\nSmart navigation ensures complete coverage and the accessible price makes it easy to justify.\", purchaseUrl: \"https://go.skimresources.com?id=1025X1701640&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dreametech.com%2Fproducts%2Fd30-ultra-ce-robot-vacuum&amp;xcust=DreameHypedeskPlacement3\", purchaseLinkText: \"Shop at Dreame\" };",
